dataset.title: A remarkable new genus and species of Rogadinae (Hymenoptera: Braconidae) of uncertain tribal placement, from Papua New Guinea, resembling Betylobraconini stat. nov.

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Butcher, Buntika A., Quicke, Donald L. J. (2015): A remarkable new genus and species of Rogadinae (Hymenoptera: Braconidae) of uncertain tribal placement, from Papua New Guinea, resembling Betylobraconini stat. nov.
